Adds a print-ready PDF for student QR badges, mirroring the staff
version. 8 badges per A4 page, school header, name, class/section,
admission_no pill, 26mm QR linking to /q/<student-uuid>.

  GET /school/students/export-qr-pdf?class_id=X&section_id=Y

Honours the same class/section filters as the existing Excel export.
"QR Badges PDF" button added to Pages/School/Students/Index.vue
header; the existing Excel button renamed to "QR Excel" to match.

Pure new feature — doesn't touch the existing Excel export logic.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
